      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STARRY RAYMAR (7) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Filled the minor placings over 457m at Q Lakeside (25.94) in a Restricted WIN but is better placed at the shorter trip here. Has a strong record at this distance including four wins. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can find winning form. LUCKY FIREBALL (2) goes very well here starting six times for two wins and two minors. Placed last time (22.37) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths. Among the main chances. SHIAN PEACHES (1) was safely held in tougher company last start at this track, but prior to that won by one length at this track (22.00) beating Good Odds Raven in a Grade 4 on February 24. Cannot be left out. CAWBOURNE SLICK (8) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone.",
